《反恐24小时》前情提要
Previously on 24

4
00:00:15,065 --> 00:00:17,013
蕾妮
Renee.

5
00:00:17,087 --> 00:00:20,023
瓦德米尔先攻击你  你是自卫
Vladimir attacked you, and you defended yourself.

6
00:00:20,023 --> 00:00:21,055
事情就是这样
That's what happened.

7
00:00:21,055 --> 00:00:22,031
要这样说吗
I don't know.

8
00:00:22,031 --> 00:00:24,080
我来证明  如果有其他任何人质疑这一点
I do, and if anybody else wants to ask you questions about that,

9
00:00:24,080 --> 00:00:26,048
我会和你站在一起回答他们
I'll be right there with you to answer them.

10
00:00:26,048 --> 00:00:28,057
你暗示了我一些丹娜的事情
You implied something about Dana.

11
00:00:28,057 --> 00:00:29,046
我想知道是什么事
I wanna know what it is.

12
00:00:29,066 --> 00:00:32,063
我想她去见了某个男人
I think she went to meet some guy.

13
00:00:32,066 --> 00:00:33,090
看一下这个
Take a look at this.

14
00:00:33,093 --> 00:00:35,013
你觉得你能找到她吗
You think you can find her?

15
00:00:36,060 --> 00:00:38,070
你答应过我  为你办完此事
You promise me I do this one thing for you,

16
00:00:38,073 --> 00:00:40,063
你就不再来烦我了
and then you'll leave me alone.

17
00:00:40,066 --> 00:00:42,060
那是不可能的
That's not gonna happen.

18
00:00:42,063 --> 00:00:44,086
我们这次可是开门红啊
This is a sweet operation that we got going here.

19
00:00:44,090 --> 00:00:47,063
知道吗  你搞到密码  然后我们下手
You know? You getting the access codes, and us pulling the jobs.

20
00:00:47,066 --> 00:00:49,030
你不能这样对我  卡文
You can't do this to me, Kevin.

21
00:00:54,089 --> 00:00:56,010
你知道我是谁吗
You know who I am?

22
00:00:57,017 --> 00:01:00,003
我只知道俄国帮派中有一个很有势力的人
All I know is that there's a very powerful man in the Russian Syndicate

23
00:01:00,006 --> 00:01:01,050
有能耐贩卖武器级别的铀
who's been trafficking weapons-grade uranium.

24
00:01:01,053 --> 00:01:02,043
你为谁卖命
Who do you work for?

25
00:01:02,046 --> 00:01:04,003
我无权告诉你
I'm not at liberty to say.

26
00:01:04,006 --> 00:01:05,069
迪米特里  给他点颜色看看
Dmitri, work on him,

27
00:01:05,069 --> 00:01:07,013
直到他准备如实招供
until he's ready to tell us everything.

28
00:01:19,080 --> 00:01:21,066
一切都结束了  你很清楚  对吧
It's over, you know that, right?

29
00:01:23,003 --> 00:01:24,026
你想知道浓缩铀棒的下落吗
You want to know where the rods are?

30
00:01:24,030 --> 00:01:25,053
我会告诉你的
I will tell you.

31
00:01:25,056 --> 00:01:27,033
但我得得到完全豁免
But I want full immunity.

32
00:01:32,056 --> 00:01:34,006
阿曼达  你看到了吗
Amanda, are you seeing this?

33
00:01:34,010 --> 00:01:35,070
浓缩铀棒在哪里
Where the hell are the rods?

34
00:01:35,073 --> 00:01:37,090
我们检测出有放射性微粒的迹象
We've picked up trace radiation signatures.

35
00:01:37,093 --> 00:01:38,083
浓缩铀棒曾放在这里
The rods were here.

36
00:01:38,086 --> 00:01:41,020
我告诉你了  浓缩铀棒在那里
I told you, they were there.

37
00:01:41,023 --> 00:01:42,096
我派了两个手下看守它们
I had two of my men guarding them.

38
00:01:43,000 --> 00:01:44,040
我们发现了他们的尸体  都被枪杀了
We found their bodies; both shot.

39
00:01:45,086 --> 00:01:47,063
我不确定是否该信你  约瑟夫
I wasn't sure I believed, Josef,

40
00:01:47,066 --> 00:01:49,000
你连自己老子都敢出卖
that you would betray your father.

41
00:01:49,003 --> 00:01:51,023
你因他拖延交货时间而惴惴不安
You were upset that he was holding up delivery of the rods.

42
00:01:51,026 --> 00:01:52,036
现在我会把它们交给你
Now I've gotten them for you.

43
00:01:52,040 --> 00:01:53,063
你什么时候能过来
When will you get here?

44
00:01:53,066 --> 00:01:54,073
五分钟之内
Less than five minutes.

45
00:01:54,076 --> 00:01:56,090
只管把我的钱准备好
Just have my money ready.

