53
00:02:51,050 --> 00:02:52,054
反恐组 我是奥布赖恩
CTU. O'Brian.

54
00:02:52,054 --> 00:02:53,030
克洛伊  我是杰克
Chloe, it's Jack.

55
00:02:53,033 --> 00:02:54,093
-黑斯廷斯在吗  -是的
- Do you have Hastings there? - Yes.

56
00:02:54,096 --> 00:02:57,003
-你准备好追踪这个电话了吗  -准备好了
- Are you ready to trace the call? - We're ready.

57
00:02:57,006 --> 00:02:58,031
巴扎耶夫只要跟他的儿子接通电话
As soon as Bazhaev gets his son on the phone,

58
00:02:58,031 --> 00:02:59,060
我们就开始对其进行三角定位
we can begin to triangulate.

59
00:02:59,060 --> 00:03:00,067
好的  别挂
Okay, hold on.

60
00:03:10,092 --> 00:03:12,089
法哈德  你在哪  你迟到了
Farhad, where are you? You're late.

61
00:03:12,092 --> 00:03:14,089
约瑟夫  是我  你爸爸
Josef, it's me, your father.

62
00:03:14,092 --> 00:03:16,049
不要挂断电话
Don't hang up. Stay on the line.

63
00:03:16,052 --> 00:03:17,072
千万不要
Please.

64
00:03:17,075 --> 00:03:19,052
我知道浓缩铀棒在你手里
I know you have the rods.

65
00:03:19,055 --> 00:03:20,072
是的
Yes.

66
00:03:20,075 --> 00:03:22,042
我就是想让你知道
I wanted you to know.

67
00:03:22,045 --> 00:03:24,035
警察也知道了  他们在这里
The police know, too. They're here.

68
00:03:24,039 --> 00:03:26,019
你告诉警察了吗
You told the police?

69
00:03:26,022 --> 00:03:27,055
当然没有
Of course not.

70
00:03:27,059 --> 00:03:29,074
是瓦德米尔的那个买主  他是联邦探员
It was Vladimir's buyer-- he's a Federal agent.

71
00:03:29,074 --> 00:03:30,099
约瑟夫  实不相瞒
Josef, just so we're up front,

72
00:03:30,099 --> 00:03:32,012
我和你父亲在一起
I'm here with your father.

73
00:03:32,015 --> 00:03:34,005
我叫杰克·鲍尔  反恐组探员
My name is Jack Bauer; I work with CTU.

74
00:03:34,009 --> 00:03:37,025
你们怎么对付他都行  我不在乎
Well, do what you want with him; I don't care.

75
00:03:37,029 --> 00:03:41,025
可能你不在乎他  但是他在乎你
Maybe you don't-- but your father cares about you.

76
00:03:41,029 --> 00:03:42,093
他跟我们商量能否赦免你
He negotiated immunity for you.

77
00:03:42,093 --> 00:03:45,037
你只要把浓缩铀棒交给我们
All you need to do is bring the fuel rods in,

78
00:03:45,040 --> 00:03:47,037
其他的事都不用你操心
and you can put the rest of this behind you.

79
00:03:47,040 --> 00:03:48,080
这是保障你安全的唯一办法
It's the only way you'll be safe.

80
00:03:48,083 --> 00:03:52,001
安全  我父亲告诉你我弟弟的事情了吗
Safe? Did my father tell you about my other brother?

81
00:03:52,001 --> 00:03:53,045
他如何对待我弟弟的
What he did to him?

82
00:03:53,045 --> 00:03:54,060
欧力格快要死了  你知道的
Oleg was dying; you know that.

83
00:03:54,063 --> 00:03:56,020
是啊  我们本可以救他
Yeah, we could have saved him.

84
00:03:56,023 --> 00:03:58,068
要不是为了你的宝贝交易  他现在还活着呢
He would be alive if not for your precious deal.

85
00:03:58,068 --> 00:04:00,082
是的  也许是这样  我不知道
You are right, maybe you are right, I don't know,

86
00:04:00,085 --> 00:04:03,067
但是... 人死不能复生
but... that doesn't bring Oleg back,

87
00:04:03,067 --> 00:04:06,032
而且我不能承受再失去一个儿子的痛苦了
and I cannot bear to lose another son.

88
00:04:06,032 --> 00:04:07,025
我不用你担心
Don't worry about me.

89
00:04:07,028 --> 00:04:09,012
-我很好  -不  你不会
- I'll be fine. - No, you won't be.

90
00:04:09,015 --> 00:04:10,065
你不会成功的
You won't be anything.

91
00:04:10,068 --> 00:04:11,098
一切都结束了
It's over.

92
00:04:12,002 --> 00:04:13,045
联邦探员在这里
Federal agents are here

93
00:04:13,048 --> 00:04:14,048
搜寻一切可能的线索
going through everything.

94
00:04:14,052 --> 00:04:17,002
整个城市都进入了警戒状态
The entire city is under guard.

95
00:04:17,005 --> 00:04:19,092
如果你不把浓缩铀棒交出来  他们会搜捕你
If you don't bring the rods in, they will hunt you down.

96
00:04:19,095 --> 00:04:21,008
他们会杀了你的  约瑟夫
They will kill you, Josef.

97
00:04:21,012 --> 00:04:23,014
我将无法保护你
I won't be able to protect you.

98
00:04:25,070 --> 00:04:27,052
我不想看见你受到伤害
I don't want to see you hurt.

99
00:04:31,097 --> 00:04:33,035
如果我把浓缩铀棒交出来
If I hand over the rods,

100
00:04:33,035 --> 00:04:34,082
该怎么做呢
how does this work?

101
00:04:34,082 --> 00:04:37,028
告诉我们你在哪里  我们会把你带回来
Tell us where you are, and we'll bring you in.

102
00:04:37,032 --> 00:04:38,078
就这样吗
Oh, just like that?

103
00:04:38,082 --> 00:04:40,032
我们以前的事就一笔勾销了吗
After everything we've done?

104
00:04:40,032 --> 00:04:42,078
是的  我告诉你了  他们会赦免我们的
Yes, I told you-- they have given us immunity.

105
00:04:43,080 --> 00:04:45,025
好吗  约瑟夫  求你了
Please, Josef, please.

106
00:04:47,012 --> 00:04:49,038
这是你最后的机会
This is your last chance.

107
00:04:51,001 --> 00:04:52,042
你在听吗
Are you there?

108
00:04:52,092 --> 00:04:54,012
是的  我在
Yes, I'm here.

109
00:04:54,015 --> 00:04:55,055
你得马上把他带回来
You need to bring him in now,

110
00:04:56,022 --> 00:04:57,052
要抢在法哈德赶到之前
before Farhad gets there.

111
00:04:57,055 --> 00:04:59,008
约瑟夫  你听见了吗
Josef, did you hear that?

112
00:04:59,012 --> 00:05:00,055
你得赶快离开
You need to move.

113
00:05:01,010 --> 00:05:02,032
约瑟夫
Josef?

114
00:05:05,044 --> 00:05:07,017
好吧  我这就过去
All right, I'm on my way.

115
00:05:07,058 --> 00:05:09,087
我在路上给你打电话  告诉你见面的地点
I'll call you from the road to let you know where to meet me.

116
00:05:09,087 --> 00:05:11,011
当心别打中浓缩铀棒
Careful with the rods.

117
00:05:14,095 --> 00:05:15,098
听起来像是枪声
Sounded like shots fired.

118
00:05:16,002 --> 00:05:17,028
你们得去救他
You need to help him!

119
00:05:17,032 --> 00:05:18,018
他在哪
Where is he?!

120
00:05:18,058 --> 00:05:19,035
不清楚
I don't know.

121
00:05:19,038 --> 00:05:20,098
克洛伊  你确定他的位置了吗
Chloe, did you get a trace on that call?

122
00:05:21,002 --> 00:05:22,068
不是很精确  不过他好像在
Not exactly, but it looks like he was

123
00:05:22,072 --> 00:05:24,082
皇后区中部的法拉盛草地公园
in central Queens near Flushing Meadow Park.

124
00:05:24,082 --> 00:05:26,068
马上派小组排查那个区域
I want units combing that area.

125
00:05:26,072 --> 00:05:28,075
-杰克  把嫌犯带回反恐组  -了解
- Jack, bring your suspect back to CTU. - Copy that.

126
00:05:28,078 --> 00:05:32,005
马上准备把他带走
Get him ready for transport now.

127
00:05:35,082 --> 00:05:37,050
-他死了吗  -是的
- Is he dead? - Yes.

128
00:05:37,050 --> 00:05:38,095
我们得抓紧时间
We need to hurry.

129
00:05:38,098 --> 00:05:40,095
船在码头上等我们
The boat is waiting for us at the port.

130
00:05:40,098 --> 00:05:42,009
去码头不是一个好主意
The port may not be the right thing.

131
00:05:42,009 --> 00:05:43,085
什么意思
What do you mean?

132
00:05:43,088 --> 00:05:45,015
当局已经知道我们的计划
The authorities know our plan.

133
00:05:45,018 --> 00:05:47,035
我们需要一个新计划
We need a new one.

134
00:05:47,038 --> 00:05:48,078
喂
Hey.

135
00:05:48,083 --> 00:05:50,095
你在干什么  别碰那东西
What are you doing? Don't touch that.

136
00:05:55,015 --> 00:05:56,025
你听到了吗
Did you get that?

137
00:05:56,028 --> 00:05:57,005
是的  杰克
Yes, Jack.

138
00:05:57,005 --> 00:05:59,008
我们在做声纹比对来确定他们的身份
We're trying to get an I.D. off the voice print.

139
00:05:59,012 --> 00:06:01,012
目前还没有什么线索锁定方位
So far, no luck locking down a location.

140
00:06:01,015 --> 00:06:04,015
明白  我们马上启程返回
Copy that. We're on our way back now.

141
00:06:13,072 --> 00:06:16,005
抓紧时间  把浓缩铀棒装到车上
We need to hurry. Take the van and get the rods...

142
00:06:16,008 --> 00:06:17,094
我们找到了跟最后说话这人吻合的声线
We've got a match for the voice at the end of the call--

143
00:06:17,094 --> 00:06:19,055
是法哈德·哈桑
Farhad Hassan.

144
00:06:19,060 --> 00:06:21,036
就是说他拿到了浓缩铀棒
So, he got his fuel rods.

145
00:06:21,040 --> 00:06:24,000
-确定另一男子身份了吗  -没有  长官
- Any I.D. On the other man we heard? - No, sir.

146
00:06:25,003 --> 00:06:27,036
黑斯廷斯先生  罗伯·维斯找你
Mr. Hastings, Rob Weiss for you.

147
00:06:28,015 --> 00:06:30,066
告诉他  我马上过来
Tell him I'll be right with him.

148
00:06:32,016 --> 00:06:34,046
告诉我巴扎耶夫预计到达的时间
Give me an ETA on Bazhaev.

149
00:06:34,050 --> 00:06:38,030
-是  长官  -他一到这里就开始审讯
- Yes, sir. - Start the interrogation as soon as he gets here.

150
00:06:44,063 --> 00:06:45,070
杰克  我是克罗伊
Jack, it's Chloe.

151
00:06:45,070 --> 00:06:46,070
黑斯廷斯想知道你的预计到达时间
Hastings wants your ETA.

152
00:06:46,073 --> 00:06:48,010
他想尽快审问巴扎耶夫
He's anxious to interrogate Bazhaev.

153
00:06:48,013 --> 00:06:49,050
我还有十五分钟就到了
I'm about 15 minutes out.

154
00:06:49,053 --> 00:06:51,026
但我不指望从他身上得到任何情报
But I wouldn't count on getting anything from him.

155
00:06:51,030 --> 00:06:52,088
如果巴扎耶夫想告诉我
If Bazhaev could have told me

156
00:06:52,088 --> 00:06:55,020
怎么抓住他的杀子仇人  他早告诉我了
how to get to the people that just killed his son, he would have.

157
00:06:55,023 --> 00:06:58,020
杰克  我听说了你的遭遇
Jack, I heard about what you went through.

158
00:06:58,070 --> 00:06:59,080
你还好吗
Are you okay?

159
00:07:01,016 --> 00:07:03,090
嗯  我很好  谢谢
Yeah, I'm fine. Thanks.

160
00:07:03,093 --> 00:07:05,050
蕾妮怎么样了
How's Renee?

161
00:07:05,053 --> 00:07:07,076
她很担心你
Pretty worried about you.

162
00:07:07,080 --> 00:07:09,063
她还在医务室
They've still got her in medical.

163
00:07:09,066 --> 00:07:12,070
你能帮我转接一下吗
Yeah. Could you patch me through to her?

164
00:07:12,073 --> 00:07:13,080
等一下
Hold on.

165
00:07:13,083 --> 00:07:15,056
好
Okay.

166
00:07:20,010 --> 00:07:21,040
蕾妮  杰克要和你说话
Renee, I have Jack.

167
00:07:23,053 --> 00:07:24,076
杰克
Jack.

168
00:07:24,080 --> 00:07:26,020
你还好吗
How are you?

169
00:07:26,023 --> 00:07:28,020
我很好  你呢
Uh, fine, I'm fine. What about you?

170
00:07:28,023 --> 00:07:29,076
我们有浓缩铀棒的线索了
We had a line on the fuel rods.

171
00:07:29,080 --> 00:07:31,056
但是线索又断了
We lost it.

172
00:07:33,003 --> 00:07:35,008
那现在有何计划
So what's the plan now?

173
00:07:35,008 --> 00:07:36,012
那还得黑斯廷斯说了算
It's Hastings' call.

174
00:07:36,012 --> 00:07:38,013
我把犯人带回反恐小组  然后我就撤了
I'm bringing the prisoner back to CTU, then I'm out.

175
00:07:38,016 --> 00:07:40,053
他们问你瓦德米尔的事了吗
They ask you about what happened, about Vladimir?

176
00:07:40,056 --> 00:07:42,013
是的  克罗伊问了
Uh, yes, Chloe did.

177
00:07:42,016 --> 00:07:43,040
是克罗伊做的任务简报吗
Chloe did the debrief?

178
00:07:44,057 --> 00:07:45,052
对  其实...
Yeah. I mean, I wouldn't...

179
00:07:45,052 --> 00:07:47,008
也不能叫任务简报
