One, you go back to prison

736
00:39:08,086 --> 00:39:11,066
罪名为盗窃财产和蓄意伤人
for grand larceny and aggravated assault.

737
00:39:11,069 --> 00:39:14,056
若我进了监狱  她也吃不了兜着走
I go back to prison, she goes back to prison.

738
00:39:15,059 --> 00:39:18,009
我猜她已经准备好去里面蹲一阵子了
My guess is, she's prepared to live with that.

739
00:39:20,003 --> 00:39:23,043
第二条路  我放你们走
Choice number two, I let you walk.

740
00:39:23,046 --> 00:39:25,059
你们留着那些钱
You keep your 100 grand

741
00:39:25,063 --> 00:39:27,049
有多少算多少
or what's left of it

742
00:39:27,053 --> 00:39:31,003
然后从哪来的回哪去
and you go back to wherever it is you came from.

743
00:39:32,023 --> 00:39:33,073
就这样吗
That's it?

744
00:39:33,076 --> 00:39:34,096
就是这样
That's it.

745
00:39:35,056 --> 00:39:38,069
但要是再让我在这城里看见你们俩
But if I ever see you in this city again...

746
00:39:39,007 --> 00:39:43,033
要是让我听说你们跨越州界
if I even hear about you crossing the state line,

747
00:39:43,036 --> 00:39:47,009
别怪我痛下杀手  翻脸不认人
I'll skip the formalities and kill you myself.

748
00:39:49,043 --> 00:39:51,073
能照办吗
Do we have a deal or not?

749
00:39:55,006 --> 00:39:56,046
没问题
Yeah.

750
00:39:57,049 --> 00:39:59,056
我们照办就是了
We got a deal.

751
00:39:59,059 --> 00:40:01,086
最好是这样
Better be sure.

752
00:40:01,089 --> 00:40:05,096
我不想再见到你们中任何一个
I don't want to see either one of you ever again.

753
00:40:24,090 --> 00:40:25,093
你要干嘛
Hey, what are you doing?

754
00:40:25,096 --> 00:40:28,039
-跟着他  -为什么
- Going after him. - Why?

755
00:40:28,043 --> 00:40:30,006
我们把他给做了
Oh, we get rid of him,

756
00:40:30,009 --> 00:40:31,086
就能再利用她重操旧业了
we're right back in business with her.

757
00:40:31,089 --> 00:40:33,029
得了吧  伙计
Come on, man.

758
00:40:33,033 --> 00:40:35,063
我们已经得手了
We got what we came for.

759
00:40:35,066 --> 00:40:37,099
比想象的多得多
We got more.

760
00:40:38,003 --> 00:40:40,066
我们... 就别再得寸进尺了
Let's just... let's not push our luck.

761
00:40:40,069 --> 00:40:41,093
好吗
All right?

762
00:40:41,096 --> 00:40:43,023
拜托了  好吗
Come on, all right?

763
00:40:43,026 --> 00:40:44,049
我们才刚刚开始呢
We're just getting started.

764
00:40:48,043 --> 00:40:51,029
我们该收手了  好吗
We're done. Okay?

765
00:40:51,033 --> 00:40:53,049
明白了吗
You got me?

766
00:41:02,063 --> 00:41:04,046
科尔
Cole.

767
00:41:04,049 --> 00:41:05,099
你刚才为我挺身而出的那一幕
What you did back there,

768
00:41:06,003 --> 00:41:07,016
我永远铭刻于心
I'll never forget it.

769
00:41:07,019 --> 00:41:08,093
回反恐小组吧
Let's just get back to CTU.

770
00:41:08,096 --> 00:41:10,005
科尔  我是真心的
Cole, I'm serious.

771
00:41:11,062 --> 00:41:12,032
谢谢
Thank you.

772
00:41:17,029 --> 00:41:18,043
科尔
Cole.

773
00:41:23,029 --> 00:41:24,043
珍妮
Jenny!

774
00:42:02,022 --> 00:42:03,018
对不起
I'm sorry.

775
